x4freetext: 6 MEV VAN DE GRAAFF AT AWRE.
PULSED BEAM OF PROTONS ON TRITIUM.
.CYLINDRICAL SAMPLES OF OVER 99 PERCENT PURE ELEMENTS.
SAMPLE DIMENSIONS GIVEN IN TABLE 1 OF PUBLICATION.
NE213 LIQUID SCINTILLATOR BIASSED AT 0.4 MEV.
TWO LONG COUNTERS TO MONITOR THE NEUTRON FLUX.
